80
00:06:14,259 --> 00:06:17,599
It can take many shapes and forms!

81
00:06:17,599 --> 00:06:24,669
Inhabitants perceive a safe and healthy environment,
are in control and facilitate the desired

82
00:06:24,669 --> 00:06:27,809
level of social interaction.

83
00:06:27,809 --> 00:06:31,800
The forms that facilitate these primary needs
are timeless.

84
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:40,439
See the example of social interaction facilitated
on a square in the old city of Gent in Belgium.

85
00:06:40,439 --> 00:06:43,629
However… one thing seems to be missing here.

86
00:06:43,629 --> 00:06:47,199
Do you have any idea?

87
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:51,379
‘Green’ an essential part of the livable
city.

88
00:06:51,379 --> 00:06:55,349
There is a positive correlation with the wellbeing
of citizens.

89
00:06:55,349 --> 00:07:00,169
‘Green’ is said to reduce stress in a
neighborhood.

90
00:07:00,169 --> 00:07:05,029
City dwellings in a green environment are
perceived as more attractive.

91
00:07:05,029 --> 00:07:08,039
Green makes a city friendly.

92
00:07:08,039 --> 00:07:12,240
This pocket park in the middle of Beijing
in China is also a nice example.

93
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:16,749
‘Green’ also has a positive relation with
other sustainability aspects.

94
00:07:16,749 --> 00:07:22,889
It facilitates a better microclimate and reduces
heat stress in a city.

95
00:07:22,889 --> 00:07:26,599
And it contributes to better air quality.

96
00:07:26,599 --> 00:07:30,159
‘Green’ plays a role in water storage.

97
00:07:30,159 --> 00:07:36,550
It contributed to a child friendly city and
can facilitate physical exercise,

98
00:07:36,550 --> 00:07:37,680
as you can see here.

99
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:41,719
It might even be combined with food production.

100
00:07:41,719 --> 00:07:47,550
Furthermore green supports environmental awareness.

101
00:07:47,550 --> 00:07:51,610
To wrap up,
designing a socially sustainable living environment

102
00:07:51,610 --> 00:07:58,419
starts from the primary needs for all,
and carefully build up the urban landscapes.

103
00:07:58,419 --> 00:08:04,529
In every step we need to safeguard an integral
approach to,

104
00:08:04,529 --> 00:08:08,149
